{"tid":637541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2女沒穿胸罩　夜路掀衣露「車頭燈」 ig瘋傳","createTime":"2018-04-22T00:47:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T04:57:00.000Z","uid":72009,"like":26,"dislike":150,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"b00cde3d51b3793da802d6c6e76e698b1bb0acfb","tid":637541,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T00:47:37.000Z","msg":"2名年輕女子騎腳踏車在路上閒晃，突然拉起上衣露出美乳，讓拍攝友人超興奮。<br />\n據《ニュース速報Japan》報導，日本網友「キケンブツ」20日凌晨在《推特》分享一段影片，內容是2名看起來約十幾二十歲的女子，坐在腳踏車上，其中一位女子掀起內衣露出No Bra美乳，而坐在後座的另一名女子也不甘示弱，也下車後掀起上衣露出No Bra美乳，讓夜色瞬間被車頭燈照亮，而拍攝的男性友人也笑著大喊「來啦來啦」、「這不妙阿」。<br />\n原po也補充說，這段影片是他友人分享在《Instagram》上，他另外轉載過來。這段影片在不到20個小時就有200萬次觀看，網友看到後也紛紛留言「這種直接掀衣的感覺反而不夠色阿」、「感覺像是外遇曝光的反擊」、「看那形狀說不定是隆乳，變性人啦」、「一定是剛喝完酒醉了才這樣」、「毫無情色美學，沒有浪漫感」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180422/640_0b177b2c73c8cfc3b4849db35f7bca61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180422%2F640_0b177b2c73c8cfc3b4849db35f7bca61.jpg&h=bef6abfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180422/640_273bb6138ac1e88e58cec6d2fd36995f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180422%2F640_273bb6138ac1e88e58cec6d2fd36995f.jpg&h=e25da619&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180422/640_263b14706be71d61862e66b325c3331f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180422%2F640_263b14706be71d61862e66b325c3331f.jpg&h=9d4f9f9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/hot/realtime/20180422/1339112\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fhot%2Frealtime%2F20180422%2F1339112&d=S%2B5kjAccK3kMDDSUh%2FjCFf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=da1fd6e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fh